Installing FastAPI

Step 1: Create a Project Folder
mkdir fastapi_course_app
cd fastapi_course_app
Step 2: Create a Virtual Environment
Windows
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
macOS or Linux
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
Step 3: Install FastAPI
The current FastAPI tutorial recommends installing FastAPI with its standard optional dependencies:
pip install "fastapi[standard]"
This installation includes the compcal development and server execution. A minimal installation can also be performed with pip install fastapi, but additional packages may then need to be installed separately.






